{"tid":22723,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"果欄賣生果個亞姐提我，遲d博多d士多啤梨會貴返，而家有買襯手","createTime":"2016-12-04T15:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T06:20:32.000Z","uid":38633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b91ec90b4619ad6d8e9d2ed3f84141135b92de4f","tid":22723,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"果欄賣生果個亞姐提我，遲d博多d士多啤梨會貴返，而家有買襯手<br />\n<br />\n心諗，遲d日本士多啤梨進入當造期，大量供應，照計應該平d至係架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我問佢，點解呢？<br />\n<br />\n果欄亞姐：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 你有沒聽過早兩個星期，博多地陷啊？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 有啊 (其實地陷果陣我就啱啱係福岡)，但係已經填平返晒啦...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 係填平返，但係地陷果度d士多啤梨無左，填返塊地都好，d士多啤梨石都無咁快生番出嚟架!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本身個人就唔係好忍得笑，所以聽到呢度就即刻走咗。<br />\n<br />\n而家心諗，其實件事好可悲。首先，點解唔可以正正經經做生意，要用埋d咁既濕9Q。其次，博多地陷果度係市區馬路。咁低質既大話竟然講得出口，香港點解變成咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9ri761h3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9ri761h3&h=65fc60f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14fe4f4b72e00a242fa340b1d5c1ff51dc5c202f","tid":22723,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈，"},{"pid":"cae48ff4b1872c622115ca1bf73ccce77680f737","tid":22723,"uid":953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b071c305ebcf34763602e9cfa9562b43b5f44f","tid":22723,"uid":16187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:20:08.000Z","msg":"未入 以為阿姐神預測日元會再次升上高位<br />\n帶動士多啤梨值格上漲"},{"pid":"d846e0d9053c4370946cd92761a97d5524a1098b","tid":22723,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:23:26.000Z","msg":"再諗下，其實個果欄亞姐講d野，真係同689同d官講果d一9樣，好似當人地係儍既咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918fbe56ad84e7fd0385ba9bdfc56ec3038d2487","tid":22723,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"依啲咪幽默 連登仔真係要學下"},{"pid":"2f16c405cf0e5f5f0191e74f4eccc37a3114f0e4","tid":22723,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依啲咪幽默 連登仔真係要學下</blockquote><br />\n擺明係騙徒喎"},{"pid":"fec2270275eb9b564f96f5f724635a47ec5b78e4","tid":22723,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:13:35.000Z","msg":"有無人有其他係果欄遇到既奇人奇事可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"4a09557bb9b53f92d9df9e17a1c30c3cc91292b2","tid":22723,"uid":351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:17:56.000Z","msg":"邊檔咁搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fded86669b3870493464803a70a442863cfb9472","tid":22723,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:23:37.000Z","msg":"畀我就駁佢一句 士多啤梨係石屎地生出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我即刻就地買盒食完係你門口播種啦"},{"pid":"ad4283ab9925e28d866c1cfc9ce06642aa60ae36","tid":22723,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:31:24.000Z","msg":"呃啲on9 c9 好work"},{"pid":"90c3d787b69c05ecc4fef345813352c5758054a2","tid":22723,"uid":52